#

Easy Pickled Red Onions

10 min
$5
20 kcal
Difficulty: 10%
Servings: 8

Dietary Tags:

VeganGluten-FreeLow-Calorie

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Condiment

Tags:

CondimentQuickPickled

Description

Bright, tangy, and perfect for adding a punch to your meals!

Ingredients

  • red onions: 2 large
  • apple cider vinegar: 1 cup
  • water: 1 cup
  • sugar: 1 tablespoon
  • salt: 1 teaspoon
  • black peppercorns: 1 teaspoon
  • bay leaf: 1
  • coriander seeds: 1/2 teaspoon
